{"tid":1100655,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鎌倉觀光局新規定，男兒當入樽名場面禁止拍照","createTime":"2019-04-10T14:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T09:52:48.000Z","uid":52127,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"597f48ada7f00b7130a4a4f76fd3819fe91ee5de","tid":1100655,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"昔日鎌倉以大佛而聞名，但自從動畫作品《男兒當入樽》面世以來，那裡的鎌倉高校前駅立即變成世界級景點，皆因動畫主題曲內有一幕電車駛過平交道，男、女主角相遇的畫面，正是以此地為背景。由於作品的粉絲都帶著打卡和朝聖的心態到鐮倉，結果引發種種問題。鎌倉市觀光課長日前宣布，由 4 月 1 日起，禁止遊客在人潮多的地方拍照，也禁止遊客邊走邊吃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2019/04/190410_banphoto_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2019%2F04%2F190410_banphoto_02.jpg&h=43477957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲經典動畫《男兒當入樽》主題曲曾出現鎌倉高校前駅旁平交道的景觀。（photo by jpninfo）<br />\n<br />\n據報道，造訪鎌倉的觀光客數量高達每年 2,000 萬。剛才提到，不少到鐮倉的旅客都會到著名的鎌倉高校前駅平交道上拍照。那裡基本上不是旅遊設施，就算是行人道亦很窄，所以大部分旅客都會走出馬路拍照，嚴重影響交通。當地觀光部門將這裡列為禁止拍攝區域，以保障所有道路使用者的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2019/04/190410_banphoto_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2019%2F04%2F190410_banphoto_03.jpg&h=8fed79c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大量遊客站在馬路上拍照，嚴重影響交通。（photo by <a href=\"http://toyokeizai.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoyokeizai.net&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTgcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=05ff5336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">toyokeizai.net</a>）<br />\n<br />\n遊客在食肆滿布的商店街購買外賣小食之後，會邊行邊吃，有時更會隨地丟垃圾，給當地居民帶來相當的困擾。因此，觀光部門也禁止遊客邊行邊吃的行為；遊客在購買食品後，應先在食肆附近範圍食完，才繼續行走。<br />\n<br />\n除此以外，觀光部門也禁止遊客切勿在山徑小道上快跑，此舉有可能令山徑上年長的市民受傷。稍後熱門景點會豎立多語言標語，提醒遊客應有的旅遊禮儀。它們補充，這些規定沒有法律效力，僅希望規範遊客的行為，不會再為當地居民帶來困擾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=24842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D24842&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTgcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=b1537ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=24842</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20190403/k10011871841000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20190403%2Fk10011871841000.html&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTgcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=df878ba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20190403/k10011871841000.html</a>"},{"pid":"05be517191a648a8e541403f8ea6a04c158fbe2b","tid":1100655,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e202c7713495bef937488a29a6e1e462a1452b95","tid":1100655,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"可以點禁"},{"pid":"4e231d80edc024872d968f8314cd8925cebcc3ef","tid":1100655,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:26:15.000Z","msg":"2047"},{"pid":"4043d46272fc2e1aaf4f825193c406b3ddef6a48","tid":1100655,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:39:44.000Z","msg":"d台狗成日吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2cb938a2e897c317339db5cf27e85e3fc8a843","tid":1100655,"uid":36820,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:42:54.000Z","msg":"有乜7 好影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77138e19a5e5bada42cd0683bf2b3ee9132c0014","tid":1100655,"uid":51932,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"去過就知幾多大陸閪見有列車就到，衝出去影，完全唔理週邊嘅車，砵尻佢哋都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e197e76a1c9a18f1627fa94bfa64dd9755872c","tid":1100655,"uid":179467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77138e19a5e5bada42cd0683bf2b3ee9132c0014","tid":1100655,"uid":51932,"like":14,"dis